Class EdgeOut

java.lang.Object
io.github.leobeaumont.Edge
io.github.leobeaumont.EdgeOut
Direct Known Subclasses:
WeightedEdgeOut
public abstract class EdgeOut extends Edge
Represents an abstract outgoing edge connecting a Transition to a Place.

EdgeOut defines the behavior common to all edges directed from a transition to a place in a Petri net. It is abstract because subclasses must specify how the edge interacts with tokens when activated.
